Quiz 13 Audio Clips

1.

1 = B : Force To Mono = Mixes down to a single channel
2 = C : Preload Audio Data = Start load the clip at level start
3 = A : Normalize = Ensures consistent volume on single channel
4 = D : Load In Background = Finish loading the level regardless of the clips load state

2. Rank the memory usage of the following decompression options(highest to lowest)

1 = B  Decompress On Load
2 = D  Compressed In Memory with PCM
3 = A  Compressed In Memory with Vorbis
4 = C  Streaming